public javax.jcr.version.Version select(javax.jcr.version.VersionHistory versionHistory)
                                 throws javax.jcr.RepositoryException
Selects a version of the given version history. If this VersionSelector is unable to select one, it can return null.

Parameters:

Returns:
A version or null.
